<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Keren Rodas — Especialista en Recursos Humanos</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=Jost:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  :root {
    --beige:     #F5EFE6;
    --nude:      #E8D5C4;
    --gold:      #C9A98A;
    --topo:      #8B6F5E;
    --choco:     #4A3728;
    --rose:      #D4A5A5;
    --rose-pale: #F0E0E0;
    --white:     #FFFCF9;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--beige);
    color: var(--choco);
    font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    cursor: none;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ── CURSOR ── */
  #cursor {
    width: 10px; height: 10px;
    background: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 50%;
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9999;
    transition: transform .15s ease, width .2s, height .2s, background .2s;
  }
  #cursor-ring {
    width: 34px; height: 34px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--rose);
    border-radius: 50%;
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9998;
    transition: transform .35s cubic-bezier(.25,.46,.45,.94), opacity .2s;
    opacity: .7;
  }
  body:hover #cursor { opacity: 1; }

  /* ── NAV ── */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; width: 100%;
    padding: 1.4rem 4rem;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    z-index: 100;
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    background: rgba(245,239,230,.82);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,169,138,.2);
    transition: background .3s;
  }
  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    letter-spacing: .18em;
    color: var(--choco);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  nav ul { list-style: none; display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; }
  nav a {
    font-size: .78rem;
    letter-spacing: .15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--topo);
    text-decoration: none;
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 3px;
  }
  nav a::after {
    content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0;
    width: 0; height: 1px;
    background: var(--gold);
    transition: width .3s ease;
  }
  nav a:hover::after { width: 100%; }
  nav a:hover { color: var(--choco); }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex; align-items: center;
    padding: 0 4rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-bg-circles {
    position: absolute; inset: 0; pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero-bg-circles span {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    opacity: .18;
    animation: floatCircle 8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .hero-bg-circles span:nth-child(1) {
    width: 500px; height: 500px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--rose), transparent);
    top: -120px; right: -80px;
    animation-delay: 0s;
  }
  .hero-bg-circles span:nth-child(2) {
    width: 300px; height: 300px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--gold), transparent);
    bottom: 60px; left: -60px;
    animation-delay: 2.5s;
  }
  .hero-bg-circles span:nth-child(3) {
    width: 200px; height: 200px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--nude), transparent);
    top: 50%; right: 25%;
    animation-delay: 5s;
  }
  @keyframes floatCircle {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) scale(1); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-30px) scale(1.05); }
  }

  .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 680px; }

  .monogram {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 11rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: transparent;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1px var(--nude);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -.02em;
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
    animation: monogramPulse 6s ease-in-out infinite;
    opacity: .35;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  @keyframes monogramPulse {
    0%, 100% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1); opacity: .35; }
    50% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.02); opacity: .45; }
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: .7rem;
    letter-spacing: .3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .8rem;
  }
  .eyebrow::before {
    content: ''; width: 32px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold);
  }

  .hero-name {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5.2rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: var(--choco);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }
  .hero-name em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--topo);
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--topo);
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 520px;
    margin-bottom: 2.8rem;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .hero-badges {
    display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .7rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.8rem;
  }
  .badge {
    font-size: .68rem;
    letter-spacing: .12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: .45rem 1.1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    color: var(--topo);
    border-radius: 100px;
    background: rgba(201,169,138,.08);
  }

  .cta-row { display: flex; gap: 1.2rem; align-items: center; }
  .btn-primary {
    padding: .8rem 2.2rem;
    background: var(--choco);
    color: var(--beige);
    font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size: .78rem;
    letter-spacing: .18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border: none;
    cursor: none;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: background .25s, transform .2s;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--topo); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .btn-outline {
    font-size: .78rem;
    letter-spacing: .15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--topo);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gold);
    padding-bottom: 2px;
    transition: color .2s;
  }
  .btn-outline:hover { color: var(--choco); }

  .scroll-line {
    position: absolute; bottom: 2.5rem; left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: .5rem;
    font-size: .65rem; letter-spacing: .2em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .scroll-line::after {
    content: '';
    width: 1px; height: 50px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--gold), transparent);
    animation: scrollDown 1.8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes scrollDown {
    0% { transform: scaleY(0); transform-origin: top; }
    50% { transform: scaleY(1); transform-origin: top; }
    51% { transform: scaleY(1); transform-origin: bottom; }
    100% { transform: scaleY(0); transform-origin: bottom; }
  }

  /* ── SECTIONS GENERAL ── */
  section { padding: 7rem 4rem; }
  .section-label {
    font-size: .65rem;
    letter-spacing: .35em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .8rem;
  }
  .section-label::after {
    content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--gold), transparent);
    max-width: 80px;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--choco);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .section-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--topo); }

  /* ── SOBRE MÍ ── */
  #sobre { background: var(--white); }
  .sobre-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .sobre-left { position: relative; }
  .sobre-frame {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 3/4;
    background: linear-gradient(145deg, var(--nude), var(--rose-pale));
    border-radius: 2px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }
  .sobre-frame-monogram {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 8rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--gold);
    opacity: .4;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .sobre-deco {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -20px; right: -20px;
    width: 120px; height: 120px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--gold);
    border-radius: 2px;
    opacity: .5;
  }
  .sobre-stats {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  .stat-box {
    padding: 1.2rem;
    background: var(--beige);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--gold);
  }
  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    color: var(--choco);
    line-height: 1;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-size: .7rem;
    letter-spacing: .1em;
    color: var(--topo);
    margin-top: .3rem;
  }
  .sobre-text p {
    font-size: .98rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--topo);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .sobre-tags {
    display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .6rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  .sobre-tag {
    font-size: .7rem;
    padding: .38rem .95rem;
    background: var(--beige);
    border: 1px solid var(--nude);
    color: var(--topo);
    border-radius: 100px;
    letter-spacing: .06em;
  }

  /* ── EXPERIENCIA ── */
  #experiencia { background: var(--beige); }
  .exp-timeline { position: relative; }
  .exp-timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0;
    width: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--gold), var(--rose), transparent);
  }
  .exp-item {
    padding: 0 0 3.5rem 3rem;
    position: relative;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateX(-20px);
    transition: opacity .6s ease, transform .6s ease;
  }
  .exp-item.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
  .exp-dot {
    position: absolute; left: -5px; top: 6px;
    width: 11px; height: 11px;
    background: var(--white);
    border: 2px solid var(--gold);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .exp-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: start; margin-bottom: .6rem; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .5rem; }
  .exp-company {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--choco);
  }
  .exp-period {
    font-size: .7rem;
    letter-spacing: .12em;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .exp-role {
    font-size: .85rem;
    color: var(--topo);
    letter-spacing: .05em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .exp-bullets { list-style: none; }
  .exp-bullets li {
    font-size: .88rem;
    color: var(--topo);
    line-height: 1.7;
    padding: .25rem 0 .25rem 1.2rem;
    position: relative;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .exp-bullets li::before {
    content: '—';
    position: absolute; left: 0;
    color: var(--rose);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* ── HABILIDADES ── */
  #habilidades { background: var(--nude); }
  .skills-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .skill-card {
    background: var(--white);
    padding: 2rem 1.8rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color .3s, transform .25s, box-shadow .3s;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
    transition: opacity .5s ease, transform .5s ease, border-color .3s, box-shadow .3s;
  }
  .skill-card.visible {
    opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0);
  }
  .skill-card:hover {
    border-bottom-color: var(--rose);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(212,165,165,.2);
  }
  .skill-card-icon {
    width: 40px; height: 40px;
    background: var(--beige);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  .skill-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--choco);
    margin-bottom: .8rem;
  }
  .skill-card p {
    font-size: .83rem;
    color: var(--topo);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .skill-bar-wrap { margin-top: 1rem; }
  .skill-bar-label {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between;
    font-size: .68rem;
    color: var(--topo);
    letter-spacing: .08em;
    margin-bottom: .35rem;
  }
  .skill-bar {
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--beige);
    border-radius: 2px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .skill-bar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--gold), var(--rose));
    border-radius: 2px;
    width: 0;
    transition: width 1.2s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);
  }

  /* ── FORMACIÓN ── */
  #formacion { background: var(--white); }
  .edu-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .edu-card {
    padding: 2.2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--nude);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: border-color .3s, box-shadow .3s;
    opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px);
    transition: opacity .5s ease, transform .5s ease, border-color .3s;
  }
  .edu-card.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  .edu-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--gold), var(--rose));
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transform-origin: left;
    transition: transform .4s ease;
  }
  .edu-card:hover { border-color: var(--rose); box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(212,165,165,.15); }
  .edu-card:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); }
  .edu-year {
    font-size: .68rem;
    letter-spacing: .18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: .6rem;
  }
  .edu-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--choco);
    margin-bottom: .4rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .edu-inst {
    font-size: .82rem;
    color: var(--topo);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ── CONTACTO ── */
  #contacto { background: var(--choco); }
  #contacto .section-label { color: var(--gold); }
  #contacto .section-label::after { background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--gold), transparent); }
  #contacto .section-title { color: var(--beige); }
  #contacto .section-title em { color: var(--gold); }
  .contact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .contact-text {
    font-size: .98rem;
    color: var(--nude);
    line-height: 1.9;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .contact-links { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.4rem; }
  .contact-link {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.2rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--nude);
    font-size: .9rem;
    transition: color .2s;
    padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,169,138,.25);
    transition: border-color .3s, background .3s, color .2s;
  }
  .contact-link:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    background: rgba(201,169,138,.08);
    color: var(--beige);
  }
  .contact-link-icon {
    width: 36px; height: 36px;
    background: rgba(201,169,138,.15);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .contact-link-label { font-size: .68rem; letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); display: block; margin-bottom: .2rem; }
  .contact-link-val { font-size: .9rem; color: var(--nude); }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    padding: 2rem 4rem;
    background: #2e1f15;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem;
  }
  footer p { font-size: .72rem; color: var(--topo); letter-spacing: .08em; }
  .footer-logo {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: .2em;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* ── REVEAL ── */
  .reveal {
    opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px);
    transition: opacity .7s ease, transform .7s ease;
  }
  .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    nav { padding: 1.2rem 2rem; }
    nav ul { gap: 1.5rem; }
    section { padding: 5rem 2rem; }
    .hero { padding: 0 2rem; }
    .sobre-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
    .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
    footer { padding: 1.5rem 2rem; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    nav ul { display: none; }
    .hero-name { font-size: 2.8rem; }
    .monogram { font-size: 7rem; }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    *, *::before, *::after { animation: none !important; transition: none !important; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- CUSTOM CURSOR -->
<div id="cursor"></div>
<div id="cursor-ring"></div>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo">KR</a>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="#sobre">Sobre mí</a></li>
    <li><a href="#experiencia">Experiencia</a></li>
    <li><a href="#habilidades">Habilidades</a></li>
    <li><a href="#formacion">Formación</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contacto">Contacto</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero" id="inicio">
  <div class="hero-bg-circles">
    <span></span><span></span><span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="monogram">KR</div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <p class="eyebrow">Especialista en Recursos Humanos</p>
    <h1 class="hero-name">Keren<br><em>Rodas Martínez</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-tagline">Más de 8 años transformando la gestión de personas en empresas corporativas y del sector financiero, con precisión operativa y enfoque en el cumplimiento laboral peruano.</p>
    <div class="hero-badges">
      <span class="badge">Administración de Personal</span>
      <span class="badge">Nómina & Planillas</span>
      <span class="badge">SUNAFIL / MINTRA</span>
      <span class="badge">Gestión del Talento</span>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-row">
      <a href="#experiencia" class="btn-primary">Ver experiencia</a>
      <a href="#contacto" class="btn-outline">Conversemos →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll-line">Scroll</div>
</section>

<!-- SOBRE MÍ -->
<section id="sobre">
  <div class="sobre-grid">
    <div class="sobre-left reveal">
      <div class="sobre-frame">
        <span class="sobre-frame-monogram">KR</span>
      </div>
      <div class="sobre-deco"></div>
      <div class="sobre-stats">
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-num">8+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">años de experiencia</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-num">3,500</div>
          <div class="stat-label">colaboradores gestionados</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-num">180+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">ingresos mensuales</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-num">75</div>
          <div class="stat-label">inspecciones SUNAFIL / año</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="sobre-text">
      <p class="section-label">Sobre mí</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Precisión, <em>compromiso</em><br>y visión estratégica</h2>
